column5:
I don't give out 5's very often, so when I do, you know it's something special. These are a select few films who got that prestigious number.

P.S., this is not a ranked list.

column2: Monty Python and the Holy Grail
It's a Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad World
The Good, the Bad and the Ugly
Birdman or (The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance)
One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest
Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb
